title: Bug 104630 - Column icons don't show up in connecting derby database
OB: When expanding the Data Source in the Avaiable Items sector by clicking the related icon, the column icons do not show up.
EB: Expected result: The table icons and column icons should be displayed when expanding the Data Source.
SR:
Steps to reproduce: 
1. Open the software and navigate to the Avaiable Items sector.
2. Locate the Data Source and click the related icon.
3. Observe that the column icons do not appear.
